# 5. Apache Security (Recommended)

Disable PHP execution inside uploads folder.

Create:

uploads/.htaccess

-----------------------
php_flag engine off

<FilesMatch "\.(php|php5|phtml)$">
    Deny from all
</FilesMatch>

-----------------------

# 6. MySQL User Creation (Production)

Instead of using root:

CREATE USER 'appuser'@'localhost'
IDENTIFIED BY 'StrongPassword@123';

GRANT SELECT, INSERT
ON secure_registration.*
TO 'appuser'@'localhost';

FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

Update `config.php`:

$username = "appuser";
$password = "StrongPassword@123";

